    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="环境准备"><a href="#环境准备" class="headerlink" title="环境准备"></a>环境准备</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo pacman -S nodejs npm typora git</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">sudo npm i -g hexo-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li>nodejs</li><li>npm</li><li>typora</li><li>git</li><li>hexo-cli</li></ul><h2 id="新建GitHub仓库"><a href="#新建GitHub仓库" class="headerlink" title="新建GitHub仓库"></a>新建GitHub仓库</h2><blockquote><p>仓库名：GitHub帐号.github.io</p></blockquote><h2 id="git配置"><a href="#git配置" class="headerlink" title="git配置"></a>git配置</h2><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.name 用户名</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.email 邮箱帐号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="添加ssh"><a href="#添加ssh" class="headerlink" title="添加ssh"></a>添加ssh</h2><ol><li><p>生成ssh，一路回车</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C 邮箱帐号</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<em>~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub</em>，复制里面的内容，也就是sshkey</p></li><li><p>进入GitHub——Settings——SSH and GPG keys——New SSH key——将上述复制的key粘帖到Key内</p></li></ol><h2 id="初始化Hexo"><a href="#初始化Hexo" class="headerlink" title="初始化Hexo"></a>初始化Hexo</h2><h3 id="创建Hexo博客"><a href="#创建Hexo博客" class="headerlink" title="创建Hexo博客"></a>创建Hexo博客</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init GitHub用户名.github.io</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="生成静态文件"><a href="#生成静态文件" class="headerlink" title="生成静态文件"></a>生成静态文件</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="启动本地服务"><a href="#启动本地服务" class="headerlink" title="启动本地服务"></a>启动本地服务</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="访问本地博客"><a href="#访问本地博客" class="headerlink" title="访问本地博客"></a>访问本地博客</h3><p><a href="http://localhost:4000" target="_blank" rel="noopener">http://localhost:4000</a></p><h2 id="配置Hexo主题"><a href="#配置Hexo主题" class="headerlink" title="配置Hexo主题"></a>配置Hexo主题</h2><h3 id="下载主题"><a href="#下载主题" class="headerlink" title="下载主题"></a>下载主题</h3><ol><li><p><a href="https://hexo.io/themes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a>下载</p></li><li><p>将下载好的主题放入<em>GitHub用户名.github.io/theme/</em></p></li></ol><h3 id="安装主题"><a href="#安装主题" class="headerlink" title="安装主题"></a>安装主题</h3><ol><li><p>打开Hexo配置<em>_config.yml</em>，搜索<strong>theme</strong>，修改为下载好的主题</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme: 主题名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="modernist主题优化"><a href="#modernist主题优化" class="headerlink" title="modernist主题优化"></a>modernist主题优化</h2><h3 id="fancybox效果"><a href="#fancybox效果" class="headerlink" title="fancybox效果"></a>fancybox效果</h3><ol><li><p>打开<em>themes/modernist/_config.yml</em>，搜索<strong>fancybox</strong>，改为true</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fancybox: true</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在文章模板中加入图片</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">photo:</span><br><span class="line">- URI</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="文章目录"><a href="#文章目录" class="headerlink" title="文章目录"></a>文章目录</h3><ol><li><p>打开<em>themes/modernist/layout/_partial/article.ejs</em>，搜索<strong>&lt;%- post.content %&gt;</strong>，在其后写入</p><figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;!--</span> <span class="string">Table</span> <span class="string">of</span> <span class="string">Contents</span> <span class="string">--&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line">&lt;%<span class="ruby"> <span class="keyword">if</span> (!index &amp;&amp; post.toc)&#123; </span>%&gt; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;div</span> <span class="string">id="toc"</span> <span class="string">class="toc-article"&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;strong</span> <span class="string">class="toc-title"&gt;目录&lt;/strong&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line">&lt;%-<span class="ruby"> toc(post.content) </span>%&gt; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;/div&gt;</span> </span><br><span class="line">&lt;%<span class="ruby"> &#125; </span>%&gt; </span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&lt;!--</span> <span class="string">以上为文章添加目录</span> <span class="string">--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>打开<em>themes/modernist/source/css/_partial/article.styl</em>，在末尾写入</p></li></ol><figure class="highlight stylus"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="selector-class">.toc-number</span> </span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attribute">display</span> none</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="写文章"><a href="#写文章" class="headerlink" title="写文章"></a>写文章</h2><h3 id="修改文章特性"><a href="#修改文章特性" class="headerlink" title="修改文章特性"></a>修改文章特性</h3><ol><li><p>打开<em>scaffolds/post.md</em>，写入：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">---</span><br><span class="line">title: &#123;&#123; title &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">date: &#123;&#123; date &#125;&#125;</span><br><span class="line">tags: </span><br><span class="line">- </span><br><span class="line">categories: </span><br><span class="line">- </span><br><span class="line">photo:</span><br><span class="line">- </span><br><span class="line">toc: true</span><br><span class="line">---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h3 id="新建文章"><a href="#新建文章" class="headerlink" title="新建文章"></a>新建文章</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new 文章名称</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="文章摘要"><a href="#文章摘要" class="headerlink" title="文章摘要"></a>文章摘要</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">以上是摘要内容 </span><br><span class="line">&lt;!-- more --&gt; </span><br><span class="line">以下为剩余内容</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h2 id=&quot;环境准备&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#环境准备&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;环境准备&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;环境准备&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;3&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo pacman -S nodejs npm typora git&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;sudo npm i -g hexo-cli&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;nodejs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;npm&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;typora&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;git&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;hexo-cli&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;新建GitHub仓库&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#新建GitHub仓库&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;新建GitHub仓库&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;新建GitHub仓库&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;仓库名：GitHub帐号.github.io&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;git配置&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#git配置&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;git配置&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;git配置&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;git config --global user.name 用户名&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;git config --global user.email 邮箱帐号&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&quot;添加ssh&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#添加ssh&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;添加ssh&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;添加ssh&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;生成ssh，一路回车&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;figure class=&quot;highlight plain&quot;&gt;&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;gutter&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td class=&quot;code&quot;&gt;&lt;pre&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;line&quot;&gt;ssh-keygen -t rsa -C 邮箱帐号&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;p&gt;打开&lt;em&gt;~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub&lt;/em&gt;，复制里面的内容，也就是sshkey&lt;/p&gt;
